+     * are removed around the {@link #keyValueSeparator(char)}. Default: {@code true}
+     *
+     * <p>For example, given the string "  k1   =   v1  ,  k2   =   v2  ", this trims around the
+     * "=" character and string boundaries: {@code [("  k1", "v1  "),("  k2", "v2  ")]}.
